Download EMBI

get_embi.Rd

Download EMBI of different countries

Usage

get_embi(periodicidad = "mensual")

Arguments

periodicidad

string with the desired periodicity options: "diario", "semanal", "mensual", "trimestral", "anual".

Value

a tibble

Examples

get_embi("diario")
